    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The problem [begins here](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/bleed/OpenRA.Game/Player.cs#L89), where `Player::ChooseCountry()` is called with the default `requiresSelectable` value of `true`. The country given in the player reference isn't selectable, so `ChooseCountry()` [defaults to using a random country](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/bleed/OpenRA.Game/Player.cs#L58).\n"
